45:24.180 --> 45:25.766
[elevator whirring, stops]

45:25.766 --> 45:27.392
How are we gonna explain
this to our investors?

45:27.392 --> 45:29.060
[papers rustle,
hand thuds on table]

45:29.060 --> 45:31.772
[Bobby] Nice space.

45:31.772 --> 45:34.649
Edgy.

45:34.649 --> 45:36.526
Mind if I take a seat?

45:36.526 --> 45:38.444
[inhales sharply]

45:38.444 --> 45:39.737
[exhales sharply]

45:41.865 --> 45:43.950
Going forward,
you might want to consider

45:43.950 --> 45:46.077
vetting your information
a little better.

45:46.077 --> 45:47.871
[Channing] Lesson learned.

45:47.871 --> 45:50.039
[sighs]

45:50.039 --> 45:51.374
I could take pleasure

45:51.374 --> 45:53.836
in watching you three
circle the drain,

45:53.836 --> 45:55.796
but I am a practical man.

45:55.796 --> 45:57.672
And there was a reason that
I hired and trained all of you

45:57.672 --> 45:59.174
in the first place.

45:59.174 --> 46:03.595
[Bobby] So...here's what
I'm prepared to do.

46:03.595 --> 46:05.680
I will seed Ionosphere --

46:05.680 --> 46:07.850
stupid fucking name,
by the way --

46:07.850 --> 46:11.311
with 250 million dollars.

46:11.311 --> 46:13.813
That should keep the lights on.

46:13.813 --> 46:15.440
You'll be required to sign

46:15.440 --> 46:17.901
non-compete
and non-solicitation agreements.

46:17.901 --> 46:21.738
We will enter into
a revenue share agreement.

46:21.738 --> 46:25.074
The current rate for seed money
is 20 to 25%,

46:25.074 --> 46:28.494
-...so why don't we call it 40?
-40?

46:28.494 --> 46:31.789
Swallow that and wash it down
with this.

46:31.789 --> 46:34.042
You will provide
total transparency.

46:34.042 --> 46:37.420
I want your trade files
sent to my office every night.

46:37.420 --> 46:39.047
There will be a limit

46:39.047 --> 46:42.467
on how much outside capital
you can raise.

46:42.467 --> 46:47.805
At no time can you manage
more than 999 million dollars.

46:47.805 --> 46:49.182
-[sighs]
-[chuckles]

46:49.182 --> 46:51.018
There will be no buy-out
to eliminate

46:51.018 --> 46:52.644
the revenue share agreement

46:52.644 --> 46:54.395
and no lock-up on my money.

46:54.395 --> 46:57.482
I can pull the plug at any time.

46:57.482 --> 47:00.443
That's the deal.
No negotiation.

47:00.443 --> 47:04.948
I'm counting to five,
and then it's off the table.

47:04.948 --> 47:07.325
-One --
-We'll do it.

