a lot already.

55:34.373 --> 55:37.126
It can be.

55:38.627 --> 55:41.464
Maybe we shouldn't
bring it up.

55:41.464 --> 55:43.591
You think? I...

55:43.591 --> 55:44.842
Well, I mean,

55:44.842 --> 55:47.386
what kind of quality of life
will he have?

55:51.682 --> 55:53.726
Best not to
bring it up then.

